{"tid":1207920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請停止關注612 reminder channel","createTime":"2019-06-12T08:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T00:25:59.000Z","uid":63651,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c90d0c2324627101bdb1cbea1e1fd1c71a06108","tid":1207920,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"❗️❗️❗️聯合聲明 ❗️❗️❗️<br />\n🛎關於612 reminder🛎<br />\n🔴聲明由以下分group admin聯合發出🔴<br />\n1.學界（8大su)<br />\n2.戰術小組<br />\n3.連登統戰部<br />\n4.scott 認證哨兵消息<br />\n5.18區各小組<br />\n6.義工車隊<br />\n<br />\n經各小組負責人討論後，由於未有任何一個小組可以確認612 reminder admin 身份。加上該admin 多次阻止計劃好的行動。<br />\n因此發出此聯合聲明，呼籲各TG 用戶停止關注該頻道，並停止轉載該頻道未經證實之資訊。<br />\n<br />\n所有認證資訊會由認可頻道[scott 認證哨兵消息]發出<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFUevqKivPWvXzP7Wg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFUevqKivPWvXzP7Wg&d=Upau0OFRhNBgg6kYd6CVyz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=1be06cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFUevqKivPWvXzP7Wg</a>"},{"pid":"bbef65fc4f3ea18610a90239b0cf6674bb44d0d0","tid":1207920,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人轉載緊"},{"pid":"56ce0d6b47faef97fedb44aa52f741e21bb52d2b","tid":1207920,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d56a369fe23fee6ce2d0e084aac03342a298e30","tid":1207920,"uid":22880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12cd8748d974ec758c13f0ed2cf57fe983a9152a","tid":1207920,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a52aadc1df61dd1ac0144a12f326e5e96597304","tid":1207920,"uid":58584,"like":0,"dislike":0,